    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Modificar y añadir información\n",
        "\n",
        "Puedo cambiar un valor existente o añadir una nueva clave al diccionario."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Uxj0skJOQeqa"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "for clave, valor in persona.items():\n",
        "  print(clave, \":\", valor)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "0Vh-McJkQcTD",
        "outputId": "ceb8b3f2-3284-428f-9a27-3adc621fe550"
      },
      "execution_count": 4,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "nombre : Carla\n",
            "edad : 31\n",
            "ciudad : Barcelona\n",
            "profesion : Futura desarrolladora\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Recorrer un diccionario\n",
        "\n",
        "Con `items()` puedo recorrer todas las claves y valores\n",
        "de un diccionario usando un bucle for."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "gzFoYE8wQ0pb"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "usuario = {\n",
        "    \"nombre\": input(\"Introduce tu nombre: \"),\n",
        "    \"edad\": input(\"Introduce tu edad: \"),\n",
        "    \"lenguaje\": \"Python\"\n",
        "\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"\\nPerfil del usuario:\")\n",
        "\n",
        "for clave, valor in usuario.items():\n",
        "  print(clave, \":\", valor)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "tgFvZSeFQzDE",
        "outputId": "b41a1a77-a4ad-4d0d-c7a3-d08fc7a8f378"
      },
      "execution_count": 5,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Introduce tu nombre: Carla\n",
            "Introduce tu edad: 30\n",
            "\n",
            "Perfil del usuario:\n",
            "nombre : Carla\n",
            "edad : 30\n",
            "lenguaje : Python\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
